high_descs: Turn around and go up to the bed in the room behind you.
Pick up the ladle with the long black handle.
Put the ladle into the round clear bowl on top of the white table.
Pick the bowl up with the spoon in the bowl.
Turn around and walk into the room behind you and then to the coffeetable on your left.
Put the bowl and spoon down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the ladle and bowl on top of the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the bed in the bedroom.
Take the ladle from the bed.
Put the ladle in the bowl.
Take the bowl with spoon in hand.
Head through the door towards the coffeetable in the hall.
Place the bowl with spoon on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Move the ladle and bowl from the bedroom to the coffee table in the hall.

high_descs: Take the spatula in the bed
Take the spatula on the bowl along with the plate
Walk back to reach the coffee table
Place both the bowl spatula on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula in the bed place both the bowl spatula on the coffee table
